<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6b04549f-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s10"><num value="10">§ 10.</num><heading> Waters in Louisiana Purchase as public highways</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">All the navigable rivers and waters in the former Territories of Orleans and Louisiana shall be and forever remain public highways.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id6b0454a0-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e">(R.S. § 5251.)</sourceCredit>
